thread.title: BRIEF-Tieto delivers case and document management system to State Treasury
thread.title_full: BRIEF-Tieto delivers case and document management system to State Treasury | Reuters

author: Reuters
title: BRIEF-Tieto delivers case and document management system to State Treasury
text:
Sept 14 Tieto Oyj :
* State Treasury in Finland chooses Tieto to deliver its case and document management system
* Delivery will take place early 2016 and agreement is valid for five years
Source text: bit.ly/1VWUY3t
Further company coverage: (Gdynia Newsroom)
